Northbound...

32:44.630 --> 32:45.931
(engine starts)

32:45.931 --> 32:47.433
(siren wailing)

32:47.433 --> 32:50.369
Relax and enjoy the ride!

32:50.369 --> 32:51.837
PILOT:
Okay, white van.
I got a white van.

32:51.837 --> 32:52.938
Here he goes, here he goes.

32:52.938 --> 32:54.406
AIR-11's over the pursuit.

32:54.406 --> 32:56.275
Eastbound on Whittier,
coming up to the overpass.

32:56.275 --> 32:58.044
I'm gonna lose him
over the overpass, guys.

32:59.711 --> 33:01.680
(siren wailing)

33:04.216 --> 33:06.085
PILOT:
And he's back now, westbound...

33:20.132 --> 33:23.035
Suspect's continuing westbound
on Whittier.

33:30.409 --> 33:32.611
PILOT:
There he goes, guys, right turn,
guys, right turn.

33:32.611 --> 33:34.446
He's gonna be northbound
on Camulus.

33:34.446 --> 33:36.448
DISPATCH:
We've got him northbound...

33:39.951 --> 33:42.454
Back up! Back up! Go!

33:46.592 --> 33:49.395
PILOT:
He's northbound
on the street Ormay.

33:50.229 --> 33:52.298
(siren wailing)

33:55.267 --> 33:59.605
PILOT:
Continuing eastbound
Barano Street past Evergreen.

34:17.055 --> 34:18.424
He's moving.

34:19.625 --> 34:20.859
He's not stopping.

34:20.859 --> 34:22.328
He's not stopping.

34:26.898 --> 34:28.334
Right.
Clear right.

34:28.334 --> 34:29.568
PILOT:
Now, gentlemen,
coming up to Fresno

34:29.568 --> 34:30.802
and it dead end's
here at Fresno.

34:30.802 --> 34:32.204
He's slowing down, guys.

34:32.204 --> 34:33.639
Get ready for a bail.
Get ready for a bail.

34:41.380 --> 34:42.981
I got officers in foot pursuit.

34:42.981 --> 34:44.183
It's gonna be southeastbound...

34:50.589 --> 34:51.790
(grunting)

34:51.790 --> 34:53.125
Stay down! Stay down!

34:54.426 --> 34:58.630
I got a male black, wearing
black over black.

35:01.600 --> 35:02.601
Stop fighting!

35:02.601 --> 35:04.069
(yells)

35:04.069 --> 35:05.271
Yeah, I'd say we got a Code 4.

35:05.271 --> 35:06.472
Did you see that?

35:08.940 --> 35:11.577
Get him up!
Let's go.

35:11.577 --> 35:13.179
(suspect roars)

35:23.555 --> 35:26.392
There's no loyalty
amongst thieves.

35:26.392 --> 35:29.528
He folded before I had
my second cup of coffee.

35:29.528 --> 35:31.096
What kind of deal
did you make?

35:31.096 --> 35:32.664
I didn't have to make one.

35:32.664 --> 35:35.634
He gave up his boys because they
left him holding the bag.

35:35.634 --> 35:39.671
Hey Lydia, you remember
my witness, Janilla?

35:39.671 --> 35:40.506
Yeah.

35:40.506 --> 35:42.641
There was
a shooting yesterday

35:42.641 --> 35:44.743
and her grandmother
took a bullet.

35:44.743 --> 35:45.811
Is she okay?

35:45.811 --> 35:46.812
Yeah.

35:46.812 --> 35:48.280
Yeah, she's tough.

35:48.280 --> 35:50.182
While she's
recuperating,

35:50.182 --> 35:51.783
Sammy's kinda playing
daddy dearest.

35:51.783 --> 35:53.452
She's living with you?

35:53.452 --> 35:56.455
Yeah. I didn't
want to, you know,

35:56.455 --> 35:57.989
let her go
through the system.

35:57.989 --> 35:59.591
I know the feeling.

35:59.591 --> 36:03.562
Anyway, I don't know how much
longer I can take care of her.

36:03.562 --> 36:05.764
My wife's not too happy
with the arrangement.

36:05.764 --> 36:07.032
I got it, Sammy.

36:07.032 --> 36:11.603
If you get into any trouble,
just... give me a call.

36:11.603 --> 36:14.706
You know, my mom's out of town
and I've got the space.

36:14.706 --> 36:16.174
Thanks.

36:27.419 --> 36:29.321
Hey, Mom, what
is it with you?

36:29.321 --> 36:30.756
You left the door
open again.

36:30.756 --> 36:31.890
I did?

36:31.890 --> 36:33.425
Yeah, you did.

36:33.425 --> 36:37.663
Geez, I'm sorry.
Will you relax?

36:37.663 --> 36:40.432
There's a lot of bad people
out there, all right?

36:40.432 --> 36:41.433
I see it every day.

36:41.433 --> 36:44.670
How sad for you,
sweetheart.

36:44.670 --> 36:46.972
You need to protect
yourself, Mom.

36:46.972 --> 36:48.407
From what?

36:48.407 --> 36:51.610
(sighs) You want me
to go into detail?

36:54.346 --> 36:55.547
Why are you
seeing him again?

36:55.547 --> 36:57.249
Why are you
letting him back?

36:59.351 --> 37:02.688
Can we just hang out
and not argue?

37:02.688 --> 37:04.556
Please?

37:04.556 --> 37:06.992
Yeah, sure. You want
to smoke a joint?

37:06.992 --> 37:10.061
For God's sakes, we did it
a couple of times.

37:10.061 --> 37:12.564
So what?
You're so uptight.

37:12.564 --> 37:14.666
I'm...
I'm "uptight"?

37:16.101 --> 37:17.603
Yes, you are.

37:17.603 --> 37:20.806
What kind of life can you have
if you close every door?

37:27.313 --> 37:28.847
(doorbell rings)

37:34.520 --> 37:38.156
Hey, stranger.
Hey.

37:38.156 --> 37:39.591
I thought
I'd stop by

37:39.591 --> 37:42.694
and maybe we could
go to dinner.

37:42.694 --> 37:44.530
I can't.

37:44.530 --> 37:48.834
Well, how about
tomorrow?

37:48.834 --> 37:50.336
I don't think so.

37:52.103 --> 37:53.572
What's going on?

37:53.572 --> 37:56.542
Lydia, I don't think
this is going to work.

37:57.743 --> 37:59.611
Look, I been wrestling
with this.

37:59.611 --> 38:03.315
You know, I even went
to see my pastor and...

38:03.315 --> 38:05.317
I tried, I just can't
get past the fact,

38:05.317 --> 38:06.552
you know, that you lied.

38:06.552 --> 38:09.755
You know, that you lied
about being a cop.

38:09.755 --> 38:11.357
Are you serious?

38:11.357 --> 38:12.791
Yeah, I mean...

38:12.791 --> 38:17.529
how can you start a relationship
based on a lie?

38:17.529 --> 38:20.198
Well, you knew that
before we slept together.

38:20.198 --> 38:22.768
Did you tell your pastor that?

38:26.171 --> 38:27.673
(scoffs)

39:15.153 --> 39:16.955
(loud rock music playing)

39:23.462 --> 39:24.663
Corona.

39:53.024 --> 39:54.793
Sorry about last time.

39:54.793 --> 39:58.664
I shoulda known coke
wasn't your thing.

40:00.566 --> 40:02.100
It's pharmaceuticals, right?

40:17.883 --> 40:18.850
Get out of here.

40:48.379 --> 40:50.649
(knocking at door)
